Saturday 23 and Sunday 24 March
  • Buses replace trains between Port Kembla, Dapto and Wollongong.

  • Daily from 1.40am to 10am, buses also replace some trains between Bomaderry, Kiama and Dapto.
  • You may need to change buses to continue your journey.
